OL,3,CFour arrested after man stabbed and
OL,4,Cschools placed on lockdown
OL,6,FTwo men and two teenage girls have
OL,7,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of
OL,8,Fattempted murder after a stabbing that
OL,9,Fsaw two schools placed on lockdown.
OL,11,FThe "serious assault" happened on
OL,12,FAlexandra Street in Tyldesley shortly
OL,13,Fbefore 9am on Friday, 13 December,
OL,14,Fwith police and paramedics attending
OL,15,Fthe scene at 8:50am.
OL,17,FThe injured man, who is in his 40s,
OL,18,Fwas taken to hospital by ambulance
OL,19,Fwhere he remains. His injuries are
OL,20,F'serious but not life-threatening"
OL,21,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) added.
