OL,3,CFour arrested after man stabbed and
OL,4,Cschools placed on lockdown
OL,6,FTwo men in their 20s, a 19-year-old
OL,7,Fwoman and a 17-year-old girl, have all
OL,8,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of
OL,9,Fattempted murder. They remain in
OL,10,Fcustody for questioning.
OL,12,FSt George's Central CE Primary School
OL,13,Fand Fred Longworth High School were
OL,14,Fplaced on lockdown in the aftermath
OL,15,Fbut GMP now say this is believed to be
OL,16,Fan "isolated incident" with "no wide
OL,17,Fthreat to the community".
