OL,4,Cschools placed on lockdown
OL,6,FA message was sent to parents of
OL,7,Fchildren at Fred Longworth High this
OL,8,Fafternoon saying: "GMP are advising
OL,9,Fthat all local schools and wider
OL,10,Fcommunity may operate as normal.
OL,12,F"Therefore, school will close at the
OL,13,Fusual time and students will be
OL,14,Freleased as normal. GMP will ensure
OL,15,Fthat there is a police presence in and
OL,16,Faround the area of the incident this
OL,17,Fevening to provide reassurance."
