OL,3,CFour arrested after man stabbed and
OL,4,Cschools placed on lockdown
OL,6,FChief Inspector Adam Wignall from
OL,7,FGMP's Wigan district said: "I would
OL,8,Flike to reassure the local community
OL,9,Fthat this is an isolated incident with
OL,10,Fno wider threat to the general public.
OL,12,F"We have arrested four individuals,
OL,13,Fand we continuing to piece together
OL,14,Fthe full circumstances that led to
OL,15,Fthis incident taking place.
OL,17,F"Our officers will remain in the area
OL,18,Ftoday over the weekend, providing
OL,19,Freassurance and they will be happy to
OL,20,Fassist with any queries you may have.
